  <name>Paths</name>
  <summary>Manage your paths and aliases</summary>
  <description>
    <p>This appllows the user to set their paths in a GUI manner, similar to what Windows offers.
      It will add your paths and aliases in your          {{if ne .Params.subMenu "true" }}
 .bashrc.d and set it up automatically if your distribution does not support it.

      Note that it will not import your existing paths.
    </p>
  </description>

